data.meta_site_name: Future of Families and Child Wellbeing Study
data.text:
The Fragile Families and Child Wellbeing Study has changed its name to The Future of Families and Child Wellbeing Study (FFCWS). Note that FFCWS articles, research briefs, working papers, books, and book chapters published or in press prior to January 2023 will contain the study’s former name. Any further reference to FFCWS should kindly observe this name change. Visit FFCWS News to learn more about this name change.

Publications Archive

This publications archive includes: published articles, unpublished reports, working papers, books, and book chapters written using the FFCWS data. Use the “Advanced Filters” below to search publications by Author, Type, Year, or Topic. Use the search box to search the full text, title, and author fields. You may also click on the title to view a paper’s abstract and full text.
